lead_paragraph: Just when things are starting to fall in place for the surging New York Mets, another key injury clouded what should have been a jubilant clubhouse after one of their biggest wins this year.

headline.print_headline: Johnson Lifts Mets Pasts Marlins 5-2; Walker Likely Done
